 & =X_{0}\left(1-\frac{t}{T}\right)+b\left(1-\frac{T-t}{T}\right)+\left(T-t\right)\intop_{0}^{t}\frac{dB_{s}}{T-s}\\
 & =X_{0}\left(1-\frac{t}{T}\right)+b\frac{t}{T}+\left(T-t\right)\intop_{0}^{t}\frac{dB_{s}}{T-s}
